The person is a 22-year-old male who identifies himself as White. He has been arrested 1 time and has been convicted. He is 6 feet 0 inches and weighs 190 lbs. He is married and is currently living with his spouse. He has a high school diploma and is enrolled in a 4-year college. He has held 2 jobs during the year.
